headline: MOTORTREND ANNOUNCES WINNERS OF THIRD ANNUAL SOFTWARE-DEFINED VEHICLE INNOVATOR AWARDS
summary: MotorTrend Group, a Warner Bros. Discovery company, has announced the winners of the third annual SDV (Software-Defined Vehicle) Innovator Awards, which were presented at the SDV Innovator Awards Gala at CES 2025 in Las Vegas, and presented in partnership with QNX, a division of BlackBerry Limited (NYSE: BB; TSX: BB), whose technology is used by countless automakers around the world.
